* Shelbyville

===Unincorporated communities===
* Arcadia
* Dreka
* Patroon
* Possum Trot

==Images==
==Politics==
An example of the political trends of rural East Texas, Shelby usually voted Democrat in the 20th century, but has turned into a Republican stronghold in the 21st.










